  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5752063">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5752063/" class="title-link">一本书、一群人、一件事——读某鹿《唐穿》有感</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5752063"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/53587150/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u53587150-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/53587150/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">橘玄雅</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-01-23"
      class="main-meta">2013-01-23 13:00:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5752063_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一本书、一群人、一件事 ——读某鹿《唐穿》有感   前言 这是一个很不靠谱的读者在读了一本很靠谱的书之后写出来的很不靠谱的随笔，基本遵循不靠谱的读者的不靠谱精神采取不靠谱的想到哪里写到哪里的不靠谱笔法，所以请诸位靠谱青年们自行无视，跟本不靠谱读者一样不靠谱的同志...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5752063/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">16有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
